=== battery.frc1721.org ===

https://battery.frc1721.org/

Django server to keep track of the state of batteries.
Made by dublu.

----- TODO

Sort and filter
Make it look better

## Development

Use `pipenv` to manage python deps and versions

```shell
pipenv install
pipenv shell
```

Spawn a development django server

```shell
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
```

## Docker Compose

```yml
version: '3.8'

services:
  django:
    image: ghcr.io/frc-1721/battery.frc1721.org:main
    container_name: battery_django
    restart: always
    env_file:
      - .env
    ports:
      - "8000:8000"
    depends_on:
      - db

  db:
    image: postgres:15
    container_name: battery_postgres
    restart: always
    environment:
      POSTGRES_DB:
      POSTGRES_USER:
      POSTGRES_PASSWORD:
    volumes:
      - postgres_data:/var/lib/postgresql/data

volumes:
  postgres_data:
```